Opposition DA Chooses De Lille as Cape Town Mayor Candidate, Times Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-03-15T05:26:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/opposition-da-chooses-de-lille-as-cape-town-mayor-candidate-times-reports.html
The Democratic Alliance,  South
Africa ’s biggest opposition party, has chosen Patricia de Lille
as its mayoral candidate for  Cape Town  after local government
elections scheduled for May 18, Johannesburg’s Times newspaper
reported, citing Helen Zille, the party leader.  The city’s current mayor is the DA’s Dan Plato.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  